---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
title="MVCC&Vacuum:PostgreSQL'sConcurrencyEngine"
description="InteractivevisualizationofPostgreSQLMVCC—tuplevisibility,deadtuples,tablebloat,VACUUM,autovacuum,andtransactionIDwraparound"
breadcrumbs={[
{label:"Home",href:"/"},
{label:"PostgreSQL",href:"/postgresql/"},
{label:"MVCC&Vacuum",href:"/postgresql/mvcc-vacuum/"}
]}
>
<div class="viz-container">
<header class="viz-header">
<h1>🔄MVCC&Vacuum</h1>
<p class="subtitle">HowPostgreSQLManagesConcurrentAccessWithoutReadLocks</p>
</header>

<!--Overview-->
<section class="overview-section">
<div class="overview-card">
<p>
PostgreSQLuses<strong>Multi-VersionConcurrencyControl</strong>(MVCC)soreadersneverblockwriters
andwritersneverblockreaders.Everyrowhashiddensystemcolumns—<em>xmin</em>(thetransaction
thatcreatedit)and<em>xmax</em>(thetransactionthatdeletedorupdatedit).AnUPDATEdoesn'tmodify
in-place:itmarkstheoldrowdeadandinsertsanewversion.Thetradeoff?<strong>Deadtuples</strong>
accumulateandneedcleanup—that'swhatVACUUMdoes.
</p>
</div>
</section>

<!--Section1:MVCCBasics—InteractiveTableHeap-->
<section class="flow-section">
<h2>📦TableHeap:TupleLifecycle</h2>
<p class="section-desc">Everyrowversionlivesintheheap.INSERTcreates,UPDATEcopies+kills,DELETEkills.</p>

<div class="flow-controls">
<button id="insertBtn" class="action-btnprimary-btn">➕INSERT</button>
<button id="updateBtn" class="action-btnstep-btn"disabled>✏️UPDATE</button>
<button id="deleteBtn" class="action-btndelete-btn"disabled>🗑️DELETE</button>
<button id="resetHeapBtn" class="action-btnreset-btn">🔄Reset</button>
</div>

<div class="flow-status" id="heapStatus">
<span class="status-badgeidle" id="heapBadge">Ready</span>
<span class="status-text" id="heapStatusText">ClickINSERTtoaddarowtotheheap</span>
</div>

<!--TableHeapVisual-->
<div class="heap-container">
<div class="heap-header">
<span class="heap-col">ctid</span>
<span class="heap-col">xmin</span>
<span class="heap-col">xmax</span>
<span class="heap-col">data</span>
<span class="heap-col">status</span>
</div>
<div class="heap-body" id="heapBody">
<div class="heap-empty">Tableisempty—INSERTsomerows!</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="heap-stats">
<div class="stat-box">
<div class="stat-value" id="liveCount">0</div>
<div class="stat-label">LiveTuples</div>
</div>
<div class="stat-boxdead">
<div class="stat-value" id="deadCount">0</div>
<div class="stat-label">DeadTuples</div>
</div>
<div class="stat-box">
<div class="stat-value" id="txnCounter">100</div>
<div class="stat-label">CurrentTxnID</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!--Explanation:Whynotupdatein-place?-->
<section class="explain-section">
<div class="explain-cardhighlight-card">
<h3>💡WhyNotUpdateIn-Place?</h3>
<p>
IfPostgreSQLmodifiedrowsdirectly,concurrentreaderswouldseehalf-writtendata.
Instead,theoldversionstaysuntouched(readersonoldersnapshotsstillseeit),
andthenewversioniswrittenelsewhere.ThisisthefundamentalMVCCtradeoff:
<strong>noreadlocks,butdeadtuplespileup</strong>.MySQLInnoDBtakesadifferent
approach—itupdatesin-placeandstoresoldversionsinanundolog.
</p>
</div>
</section>

<!--Section2:SnapshotIsolation-->
<section class="flow-section">
<h2>👁️SnapshotIsolation:WhoSeesWhat?</h2>
<p class="section-desc">EachtransactiongetsasnapshotatBEGIN.Itcanonlyseerowscommittedbeforeitssnapshot.</p>

<div class="flow-controls">
<button id="startSnapDemo" class="action-btnprimary-btn">▶RunDemo</button>
<button id="stepSnapBtn" class="action-btnstep-btn"disabled>⏭NextStep</button>
<button id="resetSnapBtn" class="action-btnreset-btn">🔄Reset</button>
</div>

<div class="snap-container">
<div class="snap-sessions">
<div class="snap-session" id="snapSession1">
<div class="snap-session-headersession-a">SessionA(Txn200)</div>
<div class="snap-session-body" id="snapBody1">
<div class="snap-empty">Waiting...</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="snap-session" id="snapSession2">
<div class="snap-session-headersession-b">SessionB(Txn201)</div>
<div class="snap-session-body" id="snapBody2">
<div class="snap-empty">Waiting...</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="snap-heap">
<div class="snap-heap-title">Table:accounts</div>
<div class="snap-heap-header">
<span>xmin</span><span>xmax</span><span>name</span><span>balance</span>
</div>
<div id="snapHeapBody" class="snap-heap-body">
<div class="snap-rowcommitted">
<span>150</span><span>—</span><span>alice</span><span>$500</span>
</div>
<div class="snap-rowcommitted">
<span>160</span><span>—</span><span>bob</span><span>$300</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="snap-explanation" id="snapExplanation">
<p>Twosessionswilloperateconcurrently.Watchhowsnapshotisolationensureseachseesaconsistentview.</p>
</div>
</section>

<!--Section3:DeadTuples&Bloat-->
<section class="flow-section">
<h2>💀DeadTuples&TableBloat</h2>
<p class="section-desc">Updatesanddeletesleavedeadtuplesbehind.WithoutVACUUM,yourtablegrowsforever.</p>

<div class="bloat-controls">
<div class="bloat-slider">
<label>Updatespersecond:<strong id="updateRateValue">10</strong></label>
<input type="range" id="updateRateSlider" min="1" max="100" value="10">
</div>
<div class="bloat-actions">
<button id="startBloatBtn" class="action-btnprimary-btn">▶StartUpdates</button>
<button id="stopBloatBtn" class="action-btnreset-btn"disabled>⏹Stop</button>
<button id="vacuumBloatBtn" class="action-btngc-btn"disabled>🧹RunVACUUM</button>
<button id="resetBloatBtn" class="action-btnreset-btn">🔄Reset</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="bloat-viz">
<div class="bloat-bar-container">
<div class="bloat-bar-label">TableSize</div>
<div class="bloat-bar-track">
<div class="bloat-bar-live" id="bloatLive" style="width:100%;">
<span>LiveData</span>
</div>
<div class="bloat-bar-dead" id="bloatDead" style="width:0%;">
<span>DeadTuples</span>
</div>
<div class="bloat-bar-free" id="bloatFree" style="width:0%;">
<span>Reusable</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bloat-meters">
<div class="bloat-meter">
<div class="meter-value" id="bloatLiveCount">100</div>
<div class="meter-label">LiveTuples</div>
</div>
<div class="bloat-meterdead">
<div class="meter-value" id="bloatDeadCount">0</div>
<div class="meter-label">DeadTuples</div>
</div>
<div class="bloat-meterfree">
<div class="meter-value" id="bloatFreeCount">0</div>
<div class="meter-label">ReusableSpace</div>
</div>
<div class="bloat-meterratio">
<div class="meter-value" id="bloatRatio">100%</div>
<div class="meter-label">SpaceEfficiency</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!--Explanation:VACUUMtypes-->
<section class="explain-section">
<div class="explain-grid">
<div class="explain-card">
<h3>🧹RegularVACUUM</h3>
<p>
Scansthetableandmarksdeadtuplesas<strong>reusable</strong>—futureINSERTs
canreclaimthatspace.Butit<em>nevershrinksthefile</em>.Atablethatgrew
to10GBstays10GBondisk,evenifmostrowsaredeleted.Runsconcurrentlywith
readsandwrites.
</p>
</div>
<div class="explain-card">
<h3>🔨VACUUMFULL</h3>
<p>
Rewritestheentiretableintoanewfile,reclaimingalldeadspace.Thefile
actuallyshrinks.Butittakesan<strong>exclusivelock</strong>—noreadsor
writesduringtheentireoperation.UseonlywhenregularVACUUMisn'tenough
andyoucanafforddowntime.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!--Section4:VACUUMAnimation-->
<section class="flow-section">
<h2>🧹VACUUMInAction</h2>
<p class="section-desc">WatchVACUUMscantheheap,identifydeadtuples,andmarkspaceasreusable.</p>

<div class="flow-controls">
<button id="setupVacuumBtn" class="action-btnprimary-btn">📦SetupTable</button>
<button id="runVacuumBtn" class="action-btngc-btn"disabled>🧹RunVACUUM</button>
<button id="resetVacuumBtn" class="action-btnreset-btn">🔄Reset</button>
</div>

<div class="vacuum-viz">
<div class="vacuum-heap" id="vacuumHeap">
<div class="heap-empty">Click"SetupTable"topopulatetheheap</div>
</div>
<div class="vacuum-progress" id="vacuumProgress" style="display:none;">
<div class="vacuum-scanner" id="vacuumScanner"></div>
<span id="vacuumProgressText">Scanning...</span>
</div>
<div class="vacuum-legend">
<span class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dotlive"></span>Live</span>
<span class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dotdead"></span>Dead</span>
<span class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dotfreed"></span>FreedbyVACUUM</span>
<span class="legend-item"><span class="legend-dotscanning"></span>Scanning</span>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!--Section5:AutovacuumThresholdCalculator-->
<section class="flow-section">
<h2>⚙️AutovacuumThresholds</h2>
<p class="section-desc">Autovacuumtriggerswhen:deadtuples≥threshold+scale_factor×totalrows</p>

<div class="autovac-controls">
<div class="autovac-slider">
<label>autovacuum_vacuum_threshold:<strong id="thresholdValue">50</strong></label>
<input type="range" id="thresholdSlider" min="0" max="500" value="50" step="10">
</div>
<div class="autovac-slider">
<label>autovacuum_vacuum_scale_factor:<strong id="scaleFactorValue">0.20</strong></label>
<input type="range" id="scaleFactorSlider" min="0" max="100" value="20" step="1">
</div>
<div class="autovac-slider">
<label>Tablerowcount:<strong id="rowCountValue">10,000</strong></label>
<input type="range" id="rowCountSlider" min="100" max="10000000" value="10000" step="100">
</div>
</div>

<div class="autovac-result">
<div class="autovac-formula">
<span class="formula-part">Trigger=</span>
<span class="formula-val" id="formulaThreshold">50</span>
<span class="formula-part">+</span>
<span class="formula-val" id="formulaScale">0.20</span>
<span class="formula-part">×</span>
<span class="formula-val" id="formulaRows">10,000</span>
<span class="formula-part">=</span>
<span class="formula-result" id="formulaResult">2,050</span>
<span class="formula-part">deadtuples</span>
</div>
<p class="autovac-desc" id="autovacDesc">
Autovacuumwilltriggerwhen2,050deadtuplesaccumulateinthistable.
</p>
</div>
</section>

<!--Section6:TransactionIDWraparound-->
<section class="flow-section">
<h2>💣TransactionIDWraparound</h2>
<p class="section-desc">PostgreSQLuses32-bittransactionIDs.At~4billion,theywraparound—anddisasterstrikes.</p>

<div class="wrap-controls">
<div class="wrap-slider">
<label>Currenttxnage:<strong id="txnAgeValue">500million</strong></label>
<input type="range" id="txnAgeSlider" min="0" max="2147483647" value="500000000" step="1000000">
</div>
<div class="wrap-actions">
<button id="ageTxnBtn" class="action-btndelete-btn">⏩Age+100M</button>
<button id="freezeBtn" class="action-btngc-btn">❄️VACUUMFREEZE</button>
<button id="resetWrapBtn" class="action-btnreset-btn">🔄Reset</button>
</div>
</div>

<div class="wrap-viz">
<div class="wrap-number-line">
<div class="wrap-track">
<div class="wrap-safe" id="wrapSafe"></div>
<div class="wrap-warning" id="wrapWarning"></div>
<div class="wrap-danger" id="wrapDanger"></div>
<div class="wrap-cursor" id="wrapCursor"></div>
</div>
<div class="wrap-labels">
<span>0</span>
<span>1B</span>
<span class="warn-label">1.5B⚠️</span>
<span class="danger-label">2B💀</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="wrap-status" id="wrapStatus">
<span class="wrap-status-icon">✅</span>
<span class="wrap-status-text">Healthy—plentyofheadroombeforewraparound</span>
</div>
<div class="wrap-info">
<div class="wrap-info-item">
<span class="wrap-info-label">Remainingbeforewraparound:</span>
<span class="wrap-info-value" id="wrapRemaining">1.65billiontxns</span>
</div>
<div class="wrap-info-item">
<span class="wrap-info-label">At1000txn/s,timeleft:</span>
<span class="wrap-info-value" id="wrapTime">~19days</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!--Explanation:Freezing-->
<section class="explain-section">
<div class="explain-cardhighlight-card">
<h3>❄️WhatIsFreezing?</h3>
<p>
WhenVACUUMfreezesatuple,itreplacesits<code>xmin</code>with<strong>FrozenTransactionId(2)</strong>,
aspecialvaluemeaning"visibletoeveryone,forever."Thisresetsthetuple'sageto0.Withoutfreezing,
oldtupleswouldeventuallyhavetheirxminwraparoundpastthecurrenttxnID—makingcommitteddata
suddenly<em>invisible</em>.PostgreSQLwill<strong>forceashutdown</strong>ratherthanletthishappen,
refusingallnewtransactionsuntilyoumanuallyrunVACUUMFREEZE.
</p>
</div>
</section>

