<p>Basedon<ahref="https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/mvcc.html" target="_blank">PostgreSQLMVCCDocumentation</a>and<ahref="https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/routine-vacuuming.html" target="_blank">RoutineVacuumingGuide</a></p>
</footer>

